sense.gloss: Japanese word constructed of elements from one or more English terms, pseudo-English word or phrase coined in Japan, wasei eigo

sdata.j: ↑何↑↓なに↓↑言↑↓い↓っても↑和製↑↓|わせい↓↑英語↑↓えいご|↓は↑日本語↑↓にほんご↓だ。
sdata.e: No matter what you say, Japanese Anglicisms are Japanese.
